attributes.review: First of all, it took the app three whole months to download. At first I thought, “maybe it’s so good that it just takes a little while” but no. When I first opened the app, this ratchet music was playing and my imaginary pet hamster passed out and was sent to the ER. Second, I got this strange dm from a guy that said he was stuck in a peach and needed me to help him out. What is that about? Like sis this isn’t James and the Giant Peach🙄. And lastly, the homepage of the app is a picture of a Cheeto looking thing. That is the last thing I wanted to see when I found out my hamster didn’t make it. So overall this app is 💩 -6287172/10 would NOT recommend.
